## 🧠 Recursive Self-Improvement (RSI)

### RSI Iteration #1 — 16/6/26 — OVER-INCLUSIVENESS BIAS
**Trigger**: User angry karena Quick Draw analysis terlalu over-inclusive (masukin semua hewan, geometric primitive, landmark kompleks).

**Rule Baru (WAJIB DITERAPKAN)**:
> **RULE RSI-1: SWEET SPOT FILTER** — HANYA include medium difficulty objects:
> - ❌ **Bukan geometric primitive**: line, circle, square, triangle → HAPUS TOTAL
> - ❌ **Bukan animal**: Semua hewan (cat, dog, elephant, dll) → BANNED
> - ❌ **Bukan landmark/kompleks ekstrem**: Eiffel Tower, Mona Lisa, aircraft carrier → BANNED
> - ✅ **FOKUS**: Everyday objects (clock, cup, hat, key, umbrella) + simple food (apple, donut, pizza) + nature (sun, moon, star, tree, flower, cloud) + basic vehicles (car, bus, bicycle)

